data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom 2-bathroom single story home on a large corner lot. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the warm and inviting living room, complete with a cozy fireplace and a soaring vaulted ceiling that adds a touch of elegance to the space. The beautifully designed galley style kitchen combines functionality and style. The efficient layout ensures that everything you need is within arms reach allowing you to prepare meals with ease! Adjacent to the kitchen you will find a welcoming dinning area. The 3 spacious bedrooms offer plenty of room for relaxation and personalization. Make sure to check out the large backyard and patio, perfect for relaxing and outdoor gatherings entertaining your family and friends. Call today to schedule your private showing! Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this your dream home!
